speedy-socials
==============

This project incorporates source code (and structural inspiration) from
third-party projects. The original sources were absorbed into the tree
during the Phase 0 transition and have since been re-implemented in
Tiger Style under `src/protocols/`. The legacy absorbed trees were
retired on 2026-05-14 (Phase 8). The attributions below remain because
the original structure and design informed the rewrite.

zat (AT Protocol Zig library)
-----------------------------
Origin: https://tangled.sh/zat.dev/zat
Author: nate nowack
License: MIT
Imported commit: 1c3eaec0f8825b47ed1390fc53872c5d12db2254 (v0.2.17-2-g1c3eaec)
Imported date: 2026-05-14
Retired date:  2026-05-14

Status: The vendored zat tree (`lib/zat/`) was removed on 2026-05-14.
Some structural patterns (MST traversal, CBOR layout, DID resolution
flow) originally drawn from zat were re-implemented from scratch under
`src/protocols/atproto/` to fit the Tiger Style + plugin contract. The
MIT attribution to nate nowack is preserved here because that early
structure informed the rewrite.

atproto (PDS scaffold, originally lib/atproto in this repo)
-----------------------------------------------------------
Origin: in-tree path dependency, authored alongside speedy-socials.
License: same as parent project (see LICENSE).
Status: Retired 2026-05-14. Re-implemented in `src/protocols/atproto/`.

See `docs/adr/003-fork-protocol-libs.md` for the retirement rationale
and `docs/phase8-retirement-inventory.md` for the file-level inventory.
